did not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33152,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/10\/mustahab-iftar-for-pilgrims\/","url_meta":{"origin":33150,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Pilgrims not fasting on the day of Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Maymunah reported: People had doubts about the fasting of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, on the day of Arafat. She sent him a cup of milk while he was standing on the plain and he drank from it while the people were looking at him. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18499,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/13\/aisha-ihram-underwear\/","url_meta":{"origin":33150,"position":2},"title":"Aisha on Ihram: Wearing underwear during the pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bukhari reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, did not see any harm in wearing an undergarment for those in her caravan traveling the pilgrimage. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1464 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Al-'Ala ibn Habib reported: I saw 'Ammar ibn Yasir, may Allah be pleased with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u